    <td valign="top">Right now I'm in the process of working on a number of new features for the website. Already I have squashed quite a few bugs and added some little stuff to make things easier. I just finished designing the search function for the site, and I'm also working on an upload script so you can use pictures and stuff in the forums, and a screenshot database that anyone can upload to and people can comment on. Also, I am getting ready to start working on a new raid planning tool that will make raid planning much easier, and will allow people to choose if they can attend or not, so that people can see a clear list of who is coming and who isn't.<br><br>The biggest problem I am having is that I don't know exactly what you guys want. I need some feedback on what type of features YOU want. Also, I need feedback on little stuff, like right now I don't know where I should put the search box. Should it be on the left side with the navagation links? and if so, where? Or should it just be on the front page under the recent posts, or just in the forums, or in a few places, or what?<br><br>PS: Sorry the website goes down sometimes. Its not my fault, the company who hosts my site SUCKS!!!<br><br>____________________<br><a href="mailto:examancer@cox.net">Examancer</a> - the admin.<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=658323" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.examancer.com/images/exapic.jpg" border=0></a>
