    <td valign="top">I want to try a raid point system. Everytime you go on a raid, you get a raid point. Once accumulated you can spend raid points to raid certain things such as epics, personal quests, and certain drops. This way there is no arguing about "He wasn't on as many raids as me...". If your on a raid that someone purchases, it is still considered as gaining a raid point.
